<font color="#ffffff"> ♪ And realize happiness is ♪
</font><font color="#5ffbff">Hạnh phúc của chúng ta vẫn là</font>

93
00:08:46,770 --> 00:08:48,600
<font color="#ffffff"> ♪ Where you are ♪
</font><font color="#5ffbff">ở ngay nơi đây!</font>

94
00:08:48,860 --> 00:08:51,510
<font color="#ffffff"> ♪  Consider the coconut (The what?) ♪
