95
00:08:51,520 --> 00:08:52,740
<font color="#ffffff"> ♪ Consider its tree ♪
</font><font color="#5ffbff">Cùng những cây dừa cao</font>

96
00:08:52,900 --> 00:08:56,280
<font color="#ffffff"> ♪ We use each part of the coconut. That's all we need ♪
