101
00:09:05,370 --> 00:09:07,120
<font color="#ffffff"> ♪ Consider the coconuts ♪
</font><font color="#5ffbff">Hãy nhìn những trái dừa này xem</font>

102
00:09:07,290 --> 00:09:09,040
<font color="#ffffff"> ♪ The trunks and the leaves ♪
</font><font color="#5ffbff">Thân cây và những lá</font>

103
00:09:09,210 --> 00:09:11,710
<font color="#ffffff"> ♪ The island gives us what we need ♪
