104
00:09:11,880 --> 00:09:13,630
<font color="#ffffff"> ♪ And no one leaves ♪
</font><font color="#5ffbff">Chẳng ai phải đi</font>

105
00:09:13,800 --> 00:09:15,260
<font color="#ffffff"> ♪ That's right, we stay ♪
</font><font color="#5ffbff">Mọi người bên nhau</font>

106
00:09:15,430 --> 00:09:17,060
<font color="#ffffff"> ♪ We're safe and we're well provided ♪
