<font color="#ffffff"> ♪ There you are ♪
</font><font color="#5ffbff">Ngay nơi đây</font>

109
00:09:21,430 --> 00:09:25,610
<font color="#ffffff"> ♪ You'll be okay. In time you'll learn just as I did ♪
