112
00:09:35,780 --> 00:09:38,140
<font color="#ffffff"> ♪  I like to dance with the water ♪
</font><font color="#5ffbff">Trước đây bà luôn thích nhảy múa cùng</font>

113
00:09:38,140 --> 00:09:39,990
<font color="#ffffff"> ♪ The undertow and the waves ♪
</font><font color="#5ffbff">Tươi xanh cùng nắng với làn gió</font>

114
00:09:40,160 --> 00:09:42,160
<font color="#ffffff"> ♪ The water is mischievous ♪
</font><font color="#5ffbff">Theo bao con sóng vỗ chơi đùa</font>

115
00:09:42,170 --> 00:09:44,170
<font color="#ffffff"> ♪ Ha! I like how it misbehaves ♪
</font><font color="#5ffbff">Tung tăng mang theo những nụ cười</font>

116
00:09:44,330 --> 00:09:46,520
<font color="#ffffff"> ♪ The village may think I'm crazy ♪
</font><font color="#5ffbff">Ở đây ai cũng nghĩ bà điên rồi</font>

117
00:09:46,520 --> 00:09:48,250
<font color="#ffffff"> ♪ Or say that I drift too far ♪
</font><font color="#5ffbff">Hay nghĩ rằng bà bơi quá xa</font>

118
00:09:48,420 --> 00:09:51,270
<font color="#ffffff"> ♪ But once you know what you like, well ♪
</font><font color="#5ffbff">Rồi con sẽ tìm được ước mơ riêng,</font>

119
00:09:51,270 --> 00:09:52,930
<font color="#ffffff"> ♪ There you are ♪
