120
00:09:54,840 --> 00:09:57,310
<font color="#ffffff"> ♪ You are your father's daughter ♪
</font><font color="#5ffbff">Người cha cùng với con</font>

121
00:09:57,310 --> 00:09:58,970
<font color="#ffffff"> ♪ Stubbornness and pride ♪
</font><font color="#5ffbff">Ngoan cường và kiêu hãnh</font>

122
00:09:59,140 --> 00:10:01,510
<font color="#ffffff"> ♪ Mind what he says but remember ♪
